Hi @natiki ,

Just implement IEntity, not IEntity&lt;TPrimaryKey&gt;. An entity can not be generic. If your Id was not int, say it was long, you should implement IEntity&lt;long&gt;

Example

<pre>public class EmailActivityEntity : EmailActivityModel,  ISoftDelete, IAudited, IEntity
{
...
}</pre>

for long Id

<pre>public class EmailActivityEntity : EmailActivityModel,  ISoftDelete, IAudited, IEntity&lt;long&gt;
{
...
}</pre>

